title: Give It Or Kick It
description:
Pablo Torre, Domonique Foxworth, and David Jacoby debate what they read into Nathaniel Hackett’s decision to take the ball out of Russell Wilson’s hands on 4th down with the game on the line, if the Cowboys should make a move for Jimmy G and they play a game of Whodunnit.

itunes:subtitle: (debatable): Hackett's decision to kick it instead of gloving the ball to Russ and should the Cowboys make a play for Jimmy G.
